再係普通既選擇題，因為你揀左死就end game，自不然大部分人都會叫你唔好死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:44:34.000Z","msg":"end game可以係好可以係壞，只係視乎你點睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:49:52.000Z","msg":"問題係未來係難以預測到。同埋好多人都會曾經有想死既念頭，如果個個想死就即刻死，分分鐘今晚就死撚曬60億人"},{"pid":"8524ff877e063934c024e2cea574bb2d22698d3e","tid":2496054,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28daf8efbd31de726d598970d6119137bbd2269e","tid":2496054,"uid":80902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:47:38.000Z","msg":"咁啱睇到篇野講呢個話題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HvkRcwS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvkRcwS.jpg&h=31e6b7ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:51:43.000Z","msg":"活著係生命嘅意義<br />\n但活著有冇意義係自己話事"},{"pid":"e8468d485a43d3324aa36f9fc6da1407fc3a635b","tid":2496054,"uid":267395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:53:01.000Z","msg":"唔敢自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />羨慕人地有勇氣自殺<br />\n自殺需要勇氣 但選擇生存係呢個人間地獄需要更大勇氣<br />\n聽過黃子華未 自殺既人就係寧願去死都唔想留係到食屎<br />\n所以個D正面講法全部都係相反立場既人鳩UP<br />\n效果同政府自殺廣告推人去死一樣<br />\n成件事係好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5321ac3c89991b8cfc475c12fa5d38167267f32c","tid":2496054,"uid":242244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83bb1a0704bc2792cb0c72c93acc35e990b3ef04","tid":2496054,"uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afb2f3cc629d27fe35fd606c8627aff493b2771b","tid":2496054,"uid":242244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"353592884c81de21c2f0bff687e661d22ad8c73f","tid":2496054,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:35:37.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n單單只係「生存」根本無難度<br />\n難係難於所面對嘅一切"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:37:54.000Z","msg":"咁你就摺啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n生存就係生存<br />\n<br />\n你加咗咁多野落去<br />\n<br />\n已經係講緊第2層次同第3層次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:46:03.000Z","msg":"點樣可以生存得嚟